The cohort definition is included so that the manifest is self-documenting. The ***manifest\_data*** component of the ***manifest*** component contains a row for each distinct combination of the requested fields in the cohort.&#x20;

Because the /***cohorts/manifest/preview*** API endpoint is always applied against the current IDC version, the idc\_data\_version in the ***cohort\_def*** is always that of the current IDC version.  This version information can be useful if the ***cohort\_def*** is saved.

